      • traverse

        public void traverse(ParamInfo.Traversal traversal,
                     Object dto)
        Traverse the value of the field on dto that is represented by this instance. If this field has a top level Optional type, traversal begins at the Optional value, or not at all if the field is empty.
        Parameters:
        traversal - traversal to apply on the values.
        dto - the object whose field will be traversed.
        See Also:
        TypeCoercer.traverse(Object, TypeCoercer.Traversal)
